{"tid":690441,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"某日，毒L小明嚮後巷執到鐵血戰士(Predator)副盔甲同裝備","createTime":"2018-06-05T01:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T01:17:37.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"801bff6a857dec87f67570caaf9fabb537f59e6c","tid":690441,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:12:30.000Z","msg":"故事世界觀<br />\n<br />\n地點:香港<br />\n<br />\n出場人物<br />\n<br />\n毒L小明(香港人類)<br />\n<br />\n咖啡色大刀 Predator  <br />\n銀色長矛Predator  <br />\n異形化Predator<br />\n<br />\n武器 (見內文，構思中)<br />\n<br />\n故事大剛<br />\n<br />\n香港係一個生活壓力好大嘅城市~日日有人吊頸同跳樓自殺！！！<br />\n毒L小明今日嚮學校比女神拒絕收生日禮物，感覺講野無人聽，去愛別人又被當透明，畢業又係等死不如提早了結自己。<br />\n小明就去平日打開 AVSP (Alien VS Predator) 街機嘅宜發大廈天台，打算終結自己一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc1c4010616031a49d2d1a18866c19cb1702ee6","tid":690441,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"剛你老母"},{"pid":"8da5d16042dbd76ebe1d85268736fc89486e2bb9","tid":690441,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"364f60a79ea1c3a2d671998539e6a21d049b4c1b","tid":690441,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:17:37.000Z","msg":"AVP，我OK呀，留名"}]}